Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.00,0:00:55.71,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fad(200,200)}だけど変わってはいけるから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.42,0:01:01.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fad(200,200)}Let's stay together　いつも
