Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.47,0:22:47.94,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fad(200,200)}素晴らしき　love & life
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.98,0:01:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看 那个人帅呆了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.75,0:01:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的耶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.85,0:01:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 他是怎么了？他不认识路吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.25,0:01:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像要去俱乐部呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.82,0:01:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去跟他搭讪吧 搞不好会找我们去玩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.33,0:01:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寒假结束了 第三学期也开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.17,0:01:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你别老是一副不可一世的样子行不行…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.51,0:01:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总有一天我要让你从嘴巴吐出对不起这三个字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.81,0:01:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.91,0:01:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是这样啦！臭小子 你真是不知羞耻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.81,0:02:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在店门口大吵大闹才是不知羞耻吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.05,0:02:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说得好 你这个娘娘腔 给我出来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.02,0:02:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我早就出来了啊 蠢猫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.79,0:02:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.36,0:02:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 本田同学 辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.43,0:02:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.60,0:02:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们两个还是老样子 感情还是那么差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.73,0:02:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新年的时候我许的愿是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.57,0:02:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“希望他们两个能和睦相处”呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.77,0:02:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来是一点效果都没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.01,0:02:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你够了吧 吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.01,0:02:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你用你的力量让我闭嘴啊 你这个娘娘腔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.38,0:02:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\an8\fs20}韭菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.08,0:02:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呜啊啊啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.22,0:02:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.99,0:02:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这下子应该会安分一点了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.49,0:02:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂—
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.59,0:02:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,澡盆的水已经放掉了 你要洗吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.13,0:02:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯…今天不洗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.36,0:02:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？不会吧——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.33,0:02:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不洗澡…好脏哟～～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.77,0:02:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想把这个家伙吊在屋顶上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.90,0:02:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩同学怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.44,0:02:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唔…好像感冒了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.94,0:03:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦！那就糟了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.58,0:03:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有点…发烧呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.65,0:03:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感冒刚开始要好好调养才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.78,0:03:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃了药之后早点去睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.25,0:03:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天最好还是请假比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.65,0:03:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系啦 用不着那样嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.29,0:03:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是明天有耐力赛跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.13,0:03:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦 还有这种比赛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.30,0:03:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天寒地冻的 年轻人可真辛苦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.57,0:03:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么耐力赛跑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.60,0:03:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.10,0:03:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,耐力赛跑马拉松…跑一大段路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.97,0:03:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,换句话说…就是胜负的较量！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.94,0:03:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！明天我就让你知道我们两个谁比较快！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可、可是…草摩同学他…好像感冒了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.15,0:03:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃个饭洗个澡就会好了！你休想逃避！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.52,0:03:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是说实在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.92,0:03:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们只要身体一虚弱的话就会很容易变身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.09,0:03:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以绝对不能逞强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.83,0:03:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.26,0:03:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好担心哦…还是希望他能够休息…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.94,0:04:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩同学…你还好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.04,0:04:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心 应该没什么问题…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.95,0:04:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是我请假的话 那个家伙又会啰唆个没完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.75,0:04:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 好像没有看到鱼谷同学呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.39,0:04:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她好像跷课了 小花在那边呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.26,0:04:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女生先跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.29,0:04:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到校门口的起跑点集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.06,0:04:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我先过去罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.70,0:04:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.20,0:04:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小花 我们今天要连小鱼的份一起加油哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.64,0:04:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊…虽然我不擅长跑步 可是我会尽力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.31,0:04:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各就各位 预备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.58,0:04:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小花!?你怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.48,0:04:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透 我已经…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.99,0:04:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跑不动了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.42,0:04:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下来只能慢慢走而已了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.62,0:05:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必担心 我会慢慢走过去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.86,0:05:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢慢走…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.50,0:05:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小花！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.17,0:05:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要走要爬都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.24,0:05:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过花岛至少也要就起跑点吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.71,0:05:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小花 你还好吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.01,0:05:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男生应该也已经就起跑位置了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.55,0:05:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩同学他…真的不要紧吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.75,0:05:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白头发！老人!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.69,0:05:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.66,0:05:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好、好年轻哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.20,0:05:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…不好意思 因为你的白头发太漂亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.96,0:05:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我以为是老人倒在路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.10,0:05:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我弄错了 真的很抱歉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.94,0:05:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知不知道草摩家？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.54,0:05:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.78,0:05:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要赢！我要打败由希！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.28,0:05:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.05,0:05:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厉害…那两个跑好快哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.28,0:05:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又不是…一百公尺赛跑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.32,0:05:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你话中有话哦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.59,0:06:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩…莫非你是草摩家的人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错 你认识吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.60,0:06:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是、是的！初次见面 我是本田…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.22,0:06:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.97,0:06:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.70,0:06:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请问…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.40,0:06:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跑过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.84,0:06:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是草摩家的人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.17,0:06:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许也是十二生肖之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.21,0:06:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请问…有什么事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.85,0:06:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.45,0:06:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.65,0:06:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上钩了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.05,0:06:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你没事吧？阿夹！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.49,0:06:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.62,0:06:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.62,0:06:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本田同学…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.69,0:06:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这个家伙 搞什么东西！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.66,0:06:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好不容易才把由希甩开的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.66,0:06:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不这么做的话 怎么能把你挡下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.43,0:06:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿春…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.10,0:06:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这种行为十分危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.30,0:06:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是发生在阿夹以外的人身上一定会受伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.27,0:06:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以绝对不能模仿哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.81,0:06:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也不能这么做啦！喂！有没有在听我说话？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.34,0:06:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这次是阿春吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.71,0:06:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陆续来找我了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.05,0:07:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不用上学吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.68,0:07:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,星期天的时候我想出去走走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果不知不觉间迷了路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.92,0:07:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等我发现的时候已经过了三天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.99,0:07:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迷路别说得理直气壮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.83,0:07:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是老样子 路痴一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.23,0:07:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很乐天的迷路人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.70,0:07:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么说来 这三天你都没有洗澡罗 脏鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.34,0:07:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看我们还是先换个地方说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.67,0:07:27.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.81,0:07:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 他叫草摩泼春
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.98,0:07:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小我们一岁 今年中学三年级
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.95,0:07:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿春 她是本田透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.28,0:07:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗 请多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.58,0:07:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…不敢当 请多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.76,0:07:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泼春很有礼貌呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.06,0:07:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起来不像中学三年级 很稳重呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 你来这里做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.16,0:07:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来打架的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.13,0:07:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.13,0:07:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,过年的时候想找你挑战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.97,0:07:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你们不是没有参加宴会吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.54,0:07:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我来找你们 好了 来吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.87,0:08:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等、等一下 我现在正在进行重要的比赛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.14,0:08:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可是花了三天的时间呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.05,0:08:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是你自己要迷路的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.68,0:08:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全搞不清楚他们在讲什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.29,0:08:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.35,0:08:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许是不太好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.65,0:08:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.25,0:08:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.49,0:08:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就照阿春的话去做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.79,0:08:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我说不行就是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.19,0:08:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点滚回去 我现在可忙得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.27,0:08:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少在那边啰哩八唆的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.67,0:08:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太慢了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.47,0:08:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是男子汉的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.61,0:08:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该是什么较量都会奉陪的 小猫咪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.51,0:08:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下地狱去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.21,0:08:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟你到底有什么深仇大恨 你要这样来妨碍我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.89,0:08:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家都称呼他是“黑春”呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.59,0:08:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,黑…黑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.09,0:08:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然阿春看起来有点迷糊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.13,0:08:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是只要他失控的话就完全不讲道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.06,0:08:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以家族的人都叫他“黑春”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.63,0:09:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么说来他和乐罗是同一型罗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.04,0:09:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.81,0:09:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的个性比乐罗还要差劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.48,0:09:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也不能在一旁看好戏 由希 你也要参加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.21,0:09:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算参加又如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.78,0:09:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起来 阿夹！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.68,0:09:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我早就站着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.05,0:09:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要去哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.42,0:09:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去战斗！战斗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.05,0:09:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本田同学 他们好像会扯很久 你还是先走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.42,0:09:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦…可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.83,0:09:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹 你什么时候变得这么拖泥带水的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.56,0:09:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫你黑春还真是一点都没错 你的个性真的很差劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.37,0:09:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少啰唆 要是你继续拖拖拉拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.24,0:09:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别怪我对那个小姐不客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.97,0:09:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？怎么个不客气法？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.77,0:09:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要这样、那样 再给她来个那样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.48,0:09:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…你说什么!?你这个混蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.05,0:09:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你忘记小时候你上厕所迷路我带你去的那份恩情了吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.75,0:09:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这个黑春真是一点也不可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.22,0:09:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是谁唤醒你体内的坏因子的？是我啊…不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.42,0:09:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那件事和这件事根本没有瓜葛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.59,0:09:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不明白你为什么要把女生牵扯进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.59,0:09:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一点关系都没有！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.13,0:09:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错 一点关系都没有！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.79,0:10:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是男人的决斗和女人没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.97,0:10:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是气死人了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.60,0:10:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个死孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.74,0:10:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是你能打倒我 随便你打哪里都没关系！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.60,0:10:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打鼻子也没关系吗？胆小鬼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你居然敢这样叫我 臭小鬼！\N本田同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.41,0:10:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫你吃不完兜着走！\N他们真的会扯很久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.14,0:10:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还是先走吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.91,0:10:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可、可、可是…应该阻止他们才对…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.15,0:10:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 花岛！你好歹也跑一下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.82,0:10:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.46,0:10:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了 我要打到罗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.50,0:10:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了 你已经被我看穿了你还不明白吗！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.63,0:10:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少啰唆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.93,0:10:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么变成格斗动画了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.64,0:10:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯…这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别理他们 本田同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.04,0:10:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们想打就让他们打好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.84,0:10:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且 我不想被卷进去遭受池鱼之殃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.84,0:10:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对不要 死也不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.55,0:11:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是刚刚看到的泼春…是那么成熟稳重啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.39,0:11:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那是什么拳啊 太轻了啦 对我完全没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.46,0:11:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要他失控的话 整个人都会变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.00,0:11:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么草摩家的人看起来都是表里不一的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.04,0:11:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你少嚣张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.17,0:11:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和由希比起来 你只不过是只鳖而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.94,0:11:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼！连比我们晚学武术的由希你都打不赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.28,0:11:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还修行个屁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.55,0:11:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逊毙了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.25,0:11:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.18,0:11:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你连鳖都不如 只是绿乌龟！水龟！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.99,0:11:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臭小子！这次真的让你下地狱！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.82,0:11:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真无聊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.76,0:11:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…看起来…好像阿夹比较厉害呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.80,0:11:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊…如果和阿春比的话 是阿夹比较厉害吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.50,0:11:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们都是格斗狂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.11,0:11:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前就很喜欢学习…武术呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.85,0:12:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦…草摩同学…草摩同学！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.28,0:12:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩同学！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.28,0:12:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.09,0:12:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发作了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.19,0:12:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 支气管…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.36,0:12:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好烫啊 感冒的时候应该多注意一点才行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.93,0:12:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先让他躺在这里吧 我马上连络本家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.57,0:12:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩同学！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.27,0:12:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像很痛苦…我应该劝他不要硬撑 多休息的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.38,0:12:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想回本家吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.68,0:12:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看这场较量暂时保留好了 阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.92,0:12:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 先到紫吴老师的家吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.22,0:12:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 耐力赛跑也要保留了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.42,0:12:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大笨蛋 害大家这么麻烦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.19,0:12:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐计程车好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.13,0:12:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行…要是由希变身的话可就麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.56,0:12:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也一起去 我什么都可以做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.97,0:12:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说得也是 有个像你这么可爱的女孩帮忙也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.51,0:12:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.27,0:13:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人说过 要抱就要抱漂亮的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.48,0:13:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.75,0:13:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了不恢复原状 你就紧紧的抱着他吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.69,0:13:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样移动他的话 由希也比较轻松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.53,0:13:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了 终于来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.83,0:13:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在讲明白好了…同花大顺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.60,0:13:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会吧！为什么你会拿到那么好的牌？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.81,0:13:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们不想跑的话就给我回去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.71,0:13:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就这个样子回来啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.95,0:13:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是笑的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.21,0:13:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,睡得很甜 看来发作的不严重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.02,0:13:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然有发烧 不过不必担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.32,0:13:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.86,0:13:51.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思 小透 你可以回学校去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.89,0:13:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用了 上学虽然重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.70,0:13:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 也不能把生病的人丢着不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.77,0:14:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈她一定也会这样对我说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.80,0:14:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而…而且…感冒是很可怕的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.67,0:14:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对不能小看感冒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.58,0:14:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那这样好了 我到学校去帮你们把书包拿回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.61,0:14:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不、不必那么麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.28,0:14:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系 没关系 阿春的事就由阿夹去连络好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.72,0:14:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么我要做这种事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.66,0:14:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泼春 最近工作太多了 变的神经紧张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.73,0:14:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要多多注意一点才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.09,0:14:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,整个家族好像得了流行性感冒似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.87,0:14:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去打电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.30,0:14:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,电话在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.47,0:14:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要光着身子到处跑啦！难看死了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.61,0:14:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我走罗 由希就麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.81,0:14:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的 拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.61,0:14:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么愉快…紫吴真的是很亲切的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.08,0:14:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女高中生～女高中生～女高中生在呼唤我～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.76,0:14:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 我知道了…麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.76,0:15:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波鸟怎么说…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.46,0:15:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他莫名其妙凶了我一顿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.77,0:15:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁叫你失踪了三天 你有什么打算？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.67,0:15:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臭由希好像已经没事了 我们继续我们的较量吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.64,0:15:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 不用了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.51,0:15:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.51,0:15:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹虽然很强 不过还是必须再锻链才行…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.25,0:15:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 小鬼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.25,0:15:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以为这样莫名其妙把人甩了就没事了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.52,0:15:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么时候变成“白春”了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.89,0:15:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？已经不是黑春了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.66,0:15:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.69,0:15:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么感觉上…好像判若两人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.26,0:15:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.13,0:15:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经睡着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.67,0:15:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别趁人家睡着的时候偷袭哦…阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.40,0:15:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁会这么做啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.74,0:15:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果用这种奸诈的手段 就算赢了 又有什么意思！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.47,0:15:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要堂堂正正的赢得胜利！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.54,0:15:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼！真不爽！我回学校去了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.92,0:15:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希和阿夹每天都会打架吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.92,0:16:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.16,0:16:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们只是每天吵架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.12,0:16:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦…他们的感情好像变好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.36,0:16:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前几乎是完全不讲话的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.40,0:16:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦…完全不讲话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.30,0:16:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 两个人好像都变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.44,0:16:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们以前的关系更紧张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.54,0:16:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在虽然会说“别靠近我”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.94,0:16:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是感觉好像比较和缓了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.45,0:16:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是因为有你在的关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.48,0:16:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我、我没有那么大的影响力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.49,0:16:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我没有一直在你们身边没有办法证实这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.76,0:16:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过他们似乎朝比较好的方向改变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.13,0:16:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样不是很好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.96,0:16:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特别是由希…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.40,0:16:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希是我的初恋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.90,0:16:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也很喜欢阿夹 但是由希对我有特别的意义…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.91,0:16:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然小时候我很讨厌他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.94,0:16:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？为什么…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.35,0:16:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为他是老鼠…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.78,0:17:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.28,0:17:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前不是传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.18,0:17:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“老鼠骑在牛背上参加宴会”吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.86,0:17:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我在潜意识里敌视他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.36,0:17:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是因为老鼠把牛当做傻瓜利用他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.40,0:17:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小时候常常被周遭的大人取笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.57,0:17:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.90,0:17:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然大人有一半是开玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.24,0:17:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我…我自己却觉得被当成傻瓜取笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.38,0:17:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会被取笑都是卑鄙的老鼠害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.45,0:17:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,于是我变成一个会迁怒的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.09,0:17:45.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人格变得阴暗也是那时造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.76,0:17:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的父母为了转移我的压力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.53,0:17:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以让我去学习武艺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.07,0:17:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全不行嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.60,0:17:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过还是无法转移
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.31,0:18:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然武艺是件很令人开心的事 可是我还是经常被取笑…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.25,0:18:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一天…我遇到了由希…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.88,0:18:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实在那之前 我从来没有跟他说过话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.42,0:18:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有在过年的时候跟他打过照面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.26,0:18:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,于是我爆发出来…累积的怨气完全发泄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.70,0:18:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最讨厌你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.63,0:18:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牛会被别人取笑都是老鼠害的 卑鄙又肮脏的老鼠害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.00,0:18:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牛会被当成傻瓜、笨蛋全都是你害的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.28,0:18:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.78,0:18:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是…这样吗…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.09,0:18:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是…笨蛋吗…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.50,0:19:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不是…才不是呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.24,0:19:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是笨蛋…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.51,0:19:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不是笨蛋呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.11,0:19:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.38,0:19:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.26,0:19:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之后我就比较少失控了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.46,0:19:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心里有什么不愉快的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.73,0:19:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就会去找由希谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.33,0:19:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他帮我解开了心头的枷锁…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.67,0:19:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希和我想像的完全不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.34,0:19:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那之前我一直认为由希是卑鄙的老鼠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.05,0:19:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还好那天有遇到由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.25,0:19:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否则 到现在我还误会他、讨厌他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.19,0:20:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那样才是真正的笨蛋呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.36,0:20:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好感人的故事哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.07,0:20:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我今天也吓了一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.80,0:20:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到由希在你身边会那么安详的笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.97,0:20:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.14,0:20:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在本家从来没有那样笑过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.44,0:20:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 我才在想是不是你让由希的心能够平静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.98,0:20:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…我没有那么大的影响力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.82,0:20:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么…我们试试看吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.62,0:20:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.29,0:20:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.43,0:20:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.93,0:20:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦…本田同学…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.06,0:20:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你醒过来了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.13,0:20:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊…我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.60,0:20:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…不好意思 给你添麻烦了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.90,0:20:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你继续睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.24,0:20:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是怎么回到家的…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.37,0:20:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泼春变成牛背你回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.17,0:20:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.35,0:20:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你…很引人侧目吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.51,0:20:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯…在你睡着的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.42,0:21:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我告诉了小透喜欢你的原因…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.66,0:21:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为什么要跟她说那些话…要是她当真了怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.36,0:21:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是真的啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.86,0:21:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个故事很感人呢…由希…同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.13,0:21:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你用不着把阿春的话当真…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.45,0:21:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你直接叫他的名字 他一定很高兴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.95,0:21:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泼春…我还是不行…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.62,0:21:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暴风般的耐力赛顺利结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.90,0:21:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那天晚上所有的人都感冒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.33,0:21:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在寒风下玩抽鬼牌 不感冒才怪…

